00:17:27.317 --> 00:17:28.917
mengatakan hal buruk
seperti itu kepada Pulkit.

00:17:31.195 --> 00:17:33.435
Saya tidak ingin hidup

00:17:34.035 --> 00:17:35.755
dimana suami
saya tidak dihormati.

00:17:42.835 --> 00:17:45.555
Ayo pergi, Pulkit.
Mari kita pulang.

00:17:46.315 --> 00:17:47.195
Ayo pergi.  - Tentu.

00:17:48.915 --> 00:17:50.515
Dewi, sebentar.

00:17:52.355 --> 00:17:53.315
Virat

